        Constructor initialize the attributes with the first three parameters and sends the rest to the super class
        Parameters:
        precipitation - the amount of precipitation predicted
        sunrise - time of expected sunrise
        sunset - time of expected sunset
        temp - the current temperature
        tempMin - the minimum predicted temperature
        tempMax - the maximum predicted temperature
        windSpeed - the expected wind speed
        windDirection - the direction the wind blows
        pressure - the current air pressure
        iconID - the string representing the icon that will be used to visually display the current weather
        description - a short description of the weather
        countryCode - The two letter code representing the country this data is from
        dt - The date time object indicating the time this was retrieved
        humidity - The amount of humidity present in this data object
